AIM:In this practical we will be going to create a telegram bot using python and telepot package

steps:

step1:Open your telegram app/web 
step2:Search for your botfather in contacts
step3:Click on /start and create your new bor (/newbot)
step4:Now you have choose your bot name(hiral08)
step5:Enter your username for your bot but it should end with 'bot'(hiral2001bot)
step6:As you will enetr username you have get your API token('1353050608:AAF3fF8UoDz9rWlU40hcrRjQjsylFRQG33k')
step7:Now you can check your bot by using methods(/getMe,/getUpate),(https://api.telegram.org/bot<your-bot-token>/getMe OR https://api.telegram.org/bot<your-bot-token>/getUpdates)
step8:Through above API you will get your chat id
step9:Now you can use others chat id and you can chat with them by using this method-
(https://api.telegram.org/bot<your-bot-token>/sendMessage?chat_id=<chat-id>&text=TestReply)
